    "name": "Saint Maker - Horror Visual Novel",
    "steam_appid": 1785300,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785300/extras/8f1641b9b6fa3ba5ff6c0f2cd64aea36.poster.avif?t=1759299025\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785300/extras/8f1641b9b6fa3ba5ff6c0f2cd64aea36.webm?t=1759299025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785300/extras/8f1641b9b6fa3ba5ff6c0f2cd64aea36.mp4?t=1759299025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是什么造就了圣人？灼其面容，伤其体肤，久病而终——历史描绘了一幅可怕的画面。在赫莉·贝尔特伦参加宗教静修时，她发现了笼罩着修道院过去的黑暗秘密。夜晚，破碎的雕像和低声的祈祷萦绕着霍莉的梦——在静修结束之前，赫莉可能要面对更多的心魔才能活着出来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当信徒做得太过火时会发生什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785300/extras/a82ec8a6c22036bf31a5b35b1a92375e.poster.avif?t=1759299025\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785300/extras/a82ec8a6c22036bf31a5b35b1a92375e.webm?t=1759299025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785300/extras/a82ec8a6c22036bf31a5b35b1a92375e.mp4?t=1759299025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✟宗教/心理恐怖：</strong>体验一个充满可怕的宗教插图和心理恐慌的恐怖故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✟简短且难忘的故事：</strong>文本大约6万字，预计游戏时间4-6小时。《鬼成圣》非常适合在黑暗的暴风雨之夜游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✟全文本配音：</strong>专业的英语配音演员为角色和他们的内心挣扎注入了生命力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✟互动对话选择：</strong>随着恐怖的展开，你的选择将帮助赫莉在这场磨难中更多地了解自己。一个普通结局和一个可解锁的额外场景等待着你发掘，剧情走向将取决于你的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✟令人毛骨悚然的视觉效果：</strong>见证圣伊德罗拉修道院的闹鬼场景，精致的背景、CG和动画插图增加了身临其境的恐怖体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✟原创配乐：</strong>原创配乐为故事增添了恐怖和情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785300/extras/91fa60632bfad951e558e158be29782f.poster.avif?t=1759299025\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785300/extras/91fa60632bfad951e558e158be29782f.webm?t=1759299025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785300/extras/91fa60632bfad951e558e158be29782f.mp4?t=1759299025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
